{
  "name": "Crafting - Base",
  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have started to develop Crafting beyond other skills, delving deeper into its possibilities.</p><p><strong>Core Feats</strong></p><ul><li>When trained: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.QLeMH5mQgh28sa5o]{Specialty Crafting}</li><li>When master: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.PiUe3tpv7UVtnfvS]{Impeccable Crafting}</li></ul><p>Choose one Skill Path and gain that path's Trained feat.</p><p><strong>Available Skill Paths</strong></p><ul><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.wE3LoKdcmVHramVM]{Remedies (Crafting) Path - Trained}</strong>: You are especially adept at crafting alchemical and magical healing potions.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.Bw0erX7sutFLWl6z]{Fieldcraft Path - Trained}</strong>: You craftsmanship is especially great when repairing equipment.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.iCdYhfmxFnFFewDU]{Alchemical Crafting Path - Trained}</strong>: You mastered alchemy, the art of creating potions.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.etEO3TloXDgbFBxM]{Magical Crafting Path - Trained}</strong>: Crafting magical items has become second nature to you.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.UIxZQWy3veeDMgwK]{Workshop Path - Trained}</strong>: More businessman than craftsman you get the best out of your workshop and it's employees.</li></ul>",
